</div>
</td>
<td style="vertical-align: middle"><b>This article contains <strong class="selflink">Persian text</strong>, written from right to left with some letters joined.</b> Without proper <a href="/wiki/Help:Arabic" title="Help:Arabic">rendering support</a>, you may see unjoined Perso-Arabic letters written left-to-right, instead of right-to-left or other symbols instead of <a href="/wiki/Perso-Arabic_script" title="Perso-Arabic script">Perso-Arabic script</a>.</td>
