akhtiari_language" title="Bakhtiari language">Bakhtiari Lori</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sangsari_language" title="Sangsari language">Sangsari</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><strong class="selflink">Persian</strong> (<a href="/wiki/Dari_(Persian)" title="Dari (Persian)" class="mw-redirect">Dari</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Tajik_language" title="Tajik language">Tajik</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Hazaragi" title="Hazaragi">Hazaragi</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Tat_language_(Caucasus)" title="Tat language (Caucasus)">Tat</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Tati_language_(Iran)" title="Tati language (Iran)" class="mw-redirect">Tati</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Zazaki_language" title="Zazaki language">Zazaki</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Dialects_of_Fars" title="Dialects of Fars">Dialects of Fars</a></span></div>
